      "writtenOn": "2026-03-11T16:52:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This regex only captures the first path segment after /redfish/v1/. If the user was trying to reach /redfish/v1/Chassis/1/Sensors/Temperature, they\u0027d be silently redirected to /redfish/v1/Chassis, losing their intended destination. There\u0027s no apparent reason to truncate the path.",
      "revId": "297e317a45d20ab6ddaf25a546ff373f8a279a50",
