      "writtenOn": "2026-03-17T10:44:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Removed the regex match(/^\\/redfish\\/v1\\/[^/]+/) entirely. The full nextPath value is now passed directly to window.location.href (after the startsWith(\u0027/redfish/v1/\u0027) safety check, so a path like /redfish/v1/Chassis/1/Sensors/Temperature reaches its intended destination without truncation.",
      "parentUuid": "56225611_d758cf06",
      "revId": "297e317a45d20ab6ddaf25a546ff373f8a279a50",
