      "writtenOn": "2026-03-11T16:52:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We should never do this, it breaks the router and causes junk to appear in the browser address bar.\n\nuse the router (like `this.$router.push(\u0027/\u0027)`) for proper SPA navigation. \n\nA manual switch to window.location.href \u003d \u0027/\u0027 causes a full page reload, destroying all Vue state and forcing a complete re-bootstrap of the application. If that is what we want, we have functions to do that.",
      "revId": "297e317a45d20ab6ddaf25a546ff373f8a279a50",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
